<br>
      <h2><span style="font-size:larger;margin:0">B</span>ehavioral <span style="font-size:larger;margin:0">O</span>bservation <span style="font-size:larger;margin:0">R</span>esearch <span style="font-size:larger;margin:0">I</span>nteractive <span style="font-size:larger;margin:0">S</span>oftware</h2>
<p>
BORIS is an easy-to-use event logging software for video/audio coding and live observations.<br>
BORIS is a free and open-source software available for GNU/Linux, Windows and Mac OS X.<br>
</p>

<p>
<a href="pages/download_linux.html"><img src="images/tux_128px.png" alt="tux logo" width="68px" style="padding-right:20px"></a>
